ke Roh''' \u2013 Sr. TE\n\n'''Mason Hampton''' \u2013 Sr. OL\n\n''Defense''\n\n'''[[Curtis Weaver]]''' \u2013 Fr. DL\n\n'''Leighton Vander Esch''' \u2013 Jr. LB\n\n'''Tyler Horton''' \u2013 Jr. DB\n\n===Mountain West second team===\n''Offense''\n\n'''[[Brett Rypien]]''' \u2013 Jr. QB\n\n'''Archie Lewis''' \u2013 Sr. OL\n\n'''Avery Williams''' \u2013 Fr. PR/KR\n\n''Defense''\n\n'''Jabril Frazier''' \u2013 Jr. DL\n\n'''David Moa''' \u2013 Jr. DL\n\n'''Kekoa Nawahine''' \u2013 So. DB\n\n'''Sean Wale''' \u2013 Sr. P\n\n===Mountain West honorable mention===\n\n'''[[Ezra Cleveland]]''' \u2013 FR. OL\n\n'''Haden Hoggarth''' \u2013 Jr. K\n\n'''[[Alexander Mattison]]''' \u2013 So. RB\n\n'''Tyson Maeva''' \u2013 So. LB\n\n'''Durrant Miles''' \u2013 Jr. DL\n\n'''John Molchon''' \u2013 So. OL\n\n'''DeAndre Pierce''' \u2013 So. DB\n\n:<small>Award Reference:<ref>{{cite web|author=MW |url=http://themw.com/documents/2017/11/29//2017_MW_Football_Honors_Release_Website.pdf |title=Mountain West Announces 2017 Football All-Conference Teams and |publisher=Themwc.com |date= |accessdate=2017-11-30}}</ref></small>\n\n==Players in the 2018 NFL Draft==\n{{see also|2018 NFL Draft}}\n{|class=\"wikitable\" width=\"80%\"\n|- align=\"center\"  style=\"{{CollegePrimaryStyle|Boise State Broncos|color=white}}\"\n| '''Player''' || '''Position''' || '''Round''' || '''Pick''' || '''NFL Club''' \n|- align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"\"\n| [[Leighton Vander Esch]] || LB || 1 || 19 ||  [[2018 Dallas Cowboys season|Dallas Cowboys]] \n|- align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"\"\n| [[Cedrick Wilson Jr.]] || WR || 6 || 208 ||  [[2018 Dallas Cowboys season|Dallas Cowboys]] \n|}\n\n{{Clear}}\n\n==Personnel==\n===Coaching staff===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"font-size:90%;\"\n|-\n! Name \n! Position \n! Consecutive seasons at<br>Boise State in current position\n|-\n| [[Bryan Harsin]] || [[Head Coach]] ||align=center| 4th\n|-\n| Kent Riddle || Associate Head Coach, [[Tight End]]s, Special Teams Coordinator ||align=center| 4th