 Potter and the Deathly Hallows&nbsp;\u2013 Part 2''\n|-\n| Best Scream-Play\n| {{won}}\n| [[Steve Kloves]]\n|-\n| Best Fantasy Actor\n| {{won}}\n| [[Daniel Radcliffe]]\n|-\n| Best Villain\n| {{won}}\n| [[Ralph Fiennes]]\n|-\n| Holy Sh*t Scene of the Year ''(Room Of Requirement)''\n| {{won}}\n| ''Harry Potter and the Deathly Hallows&nbsp;\u2013 Part 2''\n|-\n| Best F/X\n| {{won}}\n| Tim Burke\n|-\n| Best Fantasy Movie\n| {{nom}}\n| ''Harry Potter and the Deathly Hallows&nbsp;\u2013 Part 2''\n|-\n| Best Director\n|{{nom}}\n| [[David Yates]]\n|-\n| Best Fantasy Actress\n| {{nom}}\n| [[Emma Watson]]\n|-\n| Best Supporting Actor\n| {{nom}}\n| [[Rupert Grint]]\n|-\n| Best Supporting Actor\n| {{nom}}\n| [[Alan Rickman]]\n|-\n| Best Ensemble\n| {{nom}}\n| ''Harry Potter and the Deathly Hallows&nbsp;\u2013 Part 2''\n|-\n| Fight Scene of the Year ''(Final Battle)''\n| {{nom}}\n| ''Harry Potter and the Deathly Hallows&nbsp;\u2013 Part 2''\n|-\n| Fight Scene of the Year ''(The Battle of Hogwarts)''\n| {{nom}}\n| ''Harry Potter and the Deathly Hallows&nbsp;\u2013 Part 2''\n|-\n| Best 3-D Movie\n| {{nom}}\n| ''Harry Potter and the Deathly Hallows&nbsp;\u2013 Part 2''\n|-\n| [[American Film Institute Awards 2011]]\n| AFI Special Award\n|{{Won}}\n|''Harry Potter series''\n|-\n| [[World Soundtrack Academy]]\n| [[World Soundtrack Award for Soundtrack Composer of the Year|Film Composer of the Year]]\n| {{won}}\n| [[Alexandre Desplat]]\n|-\n| rowspan=57|2012\n| rowspan=3|[[84th Academy Awards|Academy Awards]]<ref name=\"Oscar\">{{cite web |title=Nominees and Winners for the 84th Academy Awards |url=http://www.oscars.org/awards/academyawards/84/nominees.html |publisher=[[Academy of Motion Picture Arts and Sciences]] |accessdate=10 October 2012}}</ref>\n| [[Academy Award for Best Production Design|Best Art Direction]]\n| {{nom}}\n| [[Stuart Craig]], Stephenie McMillan\n|-\n| [[Academy Award for Best Visual Effects|Best Visual Effects]]\n| {{nom}}\n| Tim Burke, David Vickery, Greg Butler and John Richardson\n|-\n| [[Academy Award for Best Makeup and Hairstyling|Best Makeup]]\n| {{nom}}\n| Nick Dudman, Amanda Knight, Lisa Tomblin\n|-\n|rowspan=4|[[65th British Academy Film Awards|BAFTA Awards]]<ref name=\"BAFTA\" />\n| [[BAFTA Award for Best Production Design|Best Production Design]]\n| {{nom}}\n| [[Stuart Craig]], Stephenie McMillan\n|-\n| [[BAFTA Award for Best Special Visual Effects|Best Special Visual Effects]]\n| {{won}}\n| Tim Burke, John Richardson, Greg Butler, David Vickery\n|-\n| [[BAFTA Award for Best Sound|Best Sound]]\n| {{nom}}\n| James Mather, Stuart Wilson, Stuart Hilliker, Mike Dowson, Adam Scrivener\n|-\n| [[BAFTA Award for Best Makeup and Hair|Best Makeup and Hair]]\n| {{nom}}\n| Amanda Knight, Lisa Tomblin\n|-\n| rowspan=9|[[38th People's Choice Awards|People's Choice Awards]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2011/11/08/nominations-announced-for-the-peoples-choice-awards-2012/109957/ |title=Nominations Announced for the 'People's Choice Awards 2012' |publisher=Tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com |date= |accessdate=3 November 2012}}</ref>\n| Favorite Movie\n| {{Won}}\n| ''Harry Potter and the Deathly Hallows&nbsp;\u2013 Part 2''\n|-\n| Favorite Action Movie\n| {{Won}}\n| ''Harry Potter and the Deathly Hallows&nbsp;\u2013 Part 2''\n|-\n| Favorite Movie Ensemble\n| {{Won}}\n| ''Harry Potter and the Deathly Hallows&nbsp;\u2013 Part 2''\n|-\n| Favorite Book Adaptation\n| {{won}}\n| ''Harry Potter and the Deathly Hallows&nbsp;\u2013 Part 2''\n|-\n| Favorite Movie Actor\n| {{nom}}\n| [[Daniel Radcliffe]]\n|-\n| Favorite Movie Star (''under 25'')\n| {{nom}}\n| [[Daniel Radcliffe]]\n|-\n| Favorite Movie Star (''under 25'')\n| {{nom}}\n| [[Rupert Grint]]\n|-\n| Favorite Movie Star (''under 25'')\n| {{nom}}\n| [[Emma Watson]]\n|-\n| Favorite Movie Star (''under 25'')\n| {{nom}}\n| [[Tom Felton]]\n|-\n| [[Grammy Awards]]<ref name=\"grammy2012\">{{cite web |url=http://www.nextmovie.com/blog/2012-grammy-nominations/ |title=2012 Grammy Nominations on |publisher=Nextmovie.com |date=1 December 2011 |accessdate=3 November 2012 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121212193416/http://www.nextmovie.com/blog/2012-grammy-nominations/ |archivedate=12 December 2012}}</ref>\n| [[Grammy Award for Best Score Soundtrack for Visual Media|Best Score Soundtrack for Visual Media]]\n| {{nom}}\n| Alexandre Desplat\n|-\n| rowspan=4|[[Broadcast Film Critics Association Awards]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.goldderby.com/cms/view/121 |title=Critics' Choice Awards 2011: Complete List of Nominations |publisher=Goldderby.com |date= |accessdate=3 November 2012}}</ref>\n| Best Art Direction\n| {{nom}}\n| [[Stuart Craig]]\n|-\n| Best Visual Effects\n| {{nom}}\n| Tim Burke, John Richardson, David Vickery, Greg Butler\n|-\n| Best Sound\n| {{won}}\n| ''Harry Potter and the Deathly Hallows Part 2''\n|-\n| Best Makeup\n| {{won}}\n| Nick Dudman, Amanda Knight and Mark Coulier\n|-\n|[[Screen Actors Guild]]<ref name=\"SAGAward\">{{cite web |title=SAG Awards 2012: The Winners List |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/sag-awards-2012-winners-nominees-285560 |work=[[The Hollywood Reporter]] |accessdate=9 December 2012 |date=29 January 2012}}</ref>\n| Outstanding Performance by a Stunt Ensemble in a Motion Picture\n| {{won}}\n| ''Harry Potter and the Deathly Hallows Part 2''\n|-\n| [[Costume Designers Guild Awards]]<ref>[http://costumedesignersguild.com/awards/ceremony-info/ Costume Designers Guild Local IA 892&nbsp;\u2013 14th Annual CDG Awards]. Costume Designers Guild. Retrieved 3 November 2012.</ref>\n| Excellence in Costume Design for Film&nbsp;\u2013 Fantasy\n| {{won}}\n| Jany Temime\n|-\n| [[ADG Excellence in Production Design Award]]\n| Best Art Direction for a Fantasy film\n| {{won}}\n| [[Stuart Craig]], Stephenie McMillan\n|-\n| [[Alliance of Women Film Journalists]]\n| Best Actor in a Supporting Role\n| {{nom}}\n| [[Alan Rickman]]\n|-\n| rowspan=2|[[SFX (magazine)|SFX Award]]\n| Best Film\n| {{